WEBVTT

00:20.880 --> 00:21.720
Teacher.

00:22.760 --> 00:25.440
One more matter now has some shape.

00:26.600 --> 00:30.840
If Marquis Wu'an truly lives,
what should be done?

00:37.760 --> 00:40.320
That would be a blessing for Dayin.

00:43.480 --> 00:45.560
With turmoil in the court

00:46.080 --> 00:49.200
and Prince Changxin's rebellion
at our back,

00:49.840 --> 00:53.840
Marquis Wu'an would be the pillar
that steadies the realm.

02:24.960 --> 02:29.520
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

02:49.360 --> 02:53.600
THE LATE MOTHER MENG LIHUA
THE LATE FATHER FAN ERNIU

03:09.520 --> 03:10.520
Father.

03:10.600 --> 03:11.880
Mother.

03:16.320 --> 03:17.160
Don't cry.

03:22.280 --> 03:24.880
Teacher, who lies beneath
this uninscribed stele?

03:30.960 --> 03:32.720
Today is Father's birthday.

03:33.760 --> 03:35.080
Let's smile for him.

03:35.960 --> 03:38.520
Only then will they rest in peace.

03:50.520 --> 03:53.240
Fan Erniu, Meng Lihua.

03:55.640 --> 03:56.480
Fan…

03:57.840 --> 03:59.920
Could they have used another surname?

04:01.840 --> 04:04.800
The current situation
is complex and intricate.

04:05.600 --> 04:08.200
There are too many things
beyond our control.

04:08.800 --> 04:10.240
When the time comes,

04:10.320 --> 04:12.920
I'll explain everything.

04:16.600 --> 04:17.640
It's been 16 years.

04:18.560 --> 04:22.600
The truth should finally come to light.

04:23.600 --> 04:25.840
Zheng, burn the spirit money.

04:31.520 --> 04:33.400
We still have some spirit money at home.

04:33.480 --> 04:36.120
When we get back,
burn some for your parents as well.

04:39.840 --> 04:41.080
Does burning these things

04:42.040 --> 04:43.040
really help?

04:47.120 --> 04:47.960
Of course.

04:49.760 --> 04:51.600
During festivals, people burn spirit money

04:53.000 --> 04:54.960
to tell their deceased families

04:58.400 --> 04:59.640
that we still remember them.

05:00.680 --> 05:01.840
Wenkan.

05:01.920 --> 05:03.480
You must promise me one thing.

05:04.240 --> 05:07.320
When these old bones of mine
are gone one day,

05:07.400 --> 05:10.560
you must look after
the two Fan sisters for me.

05:11.240 --> 05:13.480
Never let them get involved.

05:13.560 --> 05:16.000
Teacher, you're in good health.
Why say such things?

05:18.960 --> 05:20.400
That day will come eventually.

05:21.320 --> 05:22.200
Promise me.

05:26.040 --> 05:27.040
I give my word.

05:32.960 --> 05:34.160
Don't burn so much.

05:47.560 --> 05:48.600
Don't move.

06:07.200 --> 06:10.600
Zheng and Changyu
are like Father and Mother.

06:16.880 --> 06:17.760
Thank you.

06:19.600 --> 06:20.440
You're welcome.

06:31.040 --> 06:31.880
Come, Changning.

06:48.480 --> 06:49.320
How did you hurt your wrist?

06:50.360 --> 06:52.720
Yesterday, while hauling pigs,
the ox cart overturned.

06:53.640 --> 06:55.920
I used my hand to brace myself
and sprained it.

06:56.000 --> 06:58.280
Her wrist often hurts.

06:58.360 --> 07:00.240
Slaughtering pigs is very tiring.

07:05.000 --> 07:07.360
Repeated strain on the wrist
can inflame the tendons.

07:07.960 --> 07:09.320
Fortunately, the bone is fine.

07:11.080 --> 07:13.440
But you still need to be careful.

07:17.320 --> 07:18.360
On the way back,

07:18.440 --> 07:20.360
I'll stop by the shop
to pick something up.

07:20.960 --> 07:23.280
-Do you need money? Here.
-No, I have some.

07:24.080 --> 07:25.360
Where did you get the money?

07:28.200 --> 07:29.040
Get in first.

07:33.160 --> 07:35.240
Once you're done shopping,
head home first.

07:35.320 --> 07:36.720
I'll get some candied tangerine peel.

07:37.520 --> 07:38.360
All right.

07:39.400 --> 07:40.600
My sister is the best!

07:51.600 --> 07:52.480
You…

07:53.000 --> 07:56.040
One death after another in Xigu Alley.

07:56.120 --> 07:58.320
Who knows what unclean spirit
they've provoked.

07:58.400 --> 07:59.800
-Bad luck.
-Exactly.

07:59.880 --> 08:02.760
This little splash of rice water
won't be enough.

08:02.840 --> 08:05.560
Later, I'll go look for
dried mugwort leaves.

08:06.760 --> 08:08.920
Looks like I need to hang them
on this door.

08:09.000 --> 08:10.400
Exactly.

08:13.960 --> 08:15.760
Look at her, such an ill omen.

08:15.840 --> 08:17.080
Did you see that look she gave us?

08:21.680 --> 08:22.640
You're back?

08:26.840 --> 08:27.680
What's wrong?

08:29.760 --> 08:30.960
You look so down.

08:33.240 --> 08:34.120
Your clothes are wet.

08:35.280 --> 08:37.440
The snow was thick.
I must've gotten soaked.

08:43.000 --> 08:43.840
Wait.

08:49.520 --> 08:52.160
Did someone bully you?
Were they talking behind your back?

08:52.240 --> 08:54.680
Who would dare talk behind my back?

08:54.760 --> 08:56.200
I'd knock their teeth out.

08:57.160 --> 08:58.200
I'm going to change.

09:10.120 --> 09:12.200
Fan Changyu.

09:12.800 --> 09:14.200
Come out here, Fan Changyu!

09:15.520 --> 09:16.960
Fan Changyu, you…

09:18.760 --> 09:19.600
Fan Changyu.

09:19.680 --> 09:22.760
At noon, your little sister
pushed my Hu down the steps.

09:23.360 --> 09:24.400
Look.

09:24.480 --> 09:26.200
His two front teeth are broken.

09:26.280 --> 09:27.920
How are you going to make this right?

09:28.000 --> 09:29.360
My sister has always been frail.

09:29.960 --> 09:32.440
Your grandson is years older than her.

09:33.280 --> 09:34.560
How could she possibly push him?

09:35.160 --> 09:36.960
-Hey…
-Kang, let's talk it through.

09:37.040 --> 09:39.840
You're making a scene at the door.
Neighbors will laugh at us.

09:40.600 --> 09:42.040
The Fan family is bullying my grandson.

09:42.120 --> 09:44.440
And you think I care if they laugh at me?

09:44.520 --> 09:47.160
Children roughhouse. A few bumps
and bruises are nothing unusual.

09:47.240 --> 09:49.480
-Stop making a scene.
-Before you talk about justice,

09:50.000 --> 09:51.560
let's hear from Fan Changning.

09:52.840 --> 09:54.880
Ning, come out.

09:59.120 --> 10:00.360
Come out. It's fine.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.880
Ning, come here.

10:04.160 --> 10:05.000
Come.

10:06.280 --> 10:08.400
Changyu wants to ask
you something. Come on.

10:10.600 --> 10:11.440
Come.

10:12.240 --> 10:13.080
Let me ask you.

10:14.400 --> 10:15.560
Did you push Hu down?

10:18.480 --> 10:19.320
Look at this.

10:19.400 --> 10:21.280
Such a small child
already knows how to lie.

10:21.360 --> 10:23.760
She was nodding just now,
and now she's shaking her head.

10:25.000 --> 10:26.200
Fan Changning, answer me.

10:26.800 --> 10:27.760
Do not lie.

10:27.840 --> 10:28.960
Your mouth will rot if you do.

10:29.040 --> 10:29.960
Step aside!

10:33.760 --> 10:35.640
You dare push me?

10:36.320 --> 10:38.320
Is there no justice left in this world?

10:38.920 --> 10:41.600
The Fan family has such audacity.

10:43.080 --> 10:45.120
Look what they've done to my grandson.

10:45.200 --> 10:47.360
And she still dares to act innocent.

10:47.440 --> 10:48.360
Stop yelling!

10:48.440 --> 10:49.280
All right.

10:49.800 --> 10:52.080
Keep yelling, and I'll dunk you
headfirst into the slop bucket!

10:52.760 --> 10:53.840
I held back just now

10:54.960 --> 10:57.200
because I didn't know
who my family had offended

10:57.280 --> 10:59.440
or what trouble we'd brought
upon Xigu Alley.

10:59.520 --> 11:00.720
I owe the neighbors an apology,

11:01.720 --> 11:03.000
but not you.

11:03.840 --> 11:06.720
People keep dying in your family lately.

11:06.800 --> 11:09.680
Who in this lane doesn't know
you're the one bringing misfortune?

11:09.760 --> 11:12.000
You and Song gossip about me every day.

11:12.600 --> 11:13.840
Do you think I don't know?

11:15.040 --> 11:15.960
Fine.

11:19.680 --> 11:21.440
Today I'll give you what you want.

11:23.040 --> 11:24.240
What are you doing?

11:25.240 --> 11:27.120
Neighbors are watching.

11:27.200 --> 11:28.760
Are you going to resort to violence?

11:28.840 --> 11:31.520
You've already ruined my reputation
with your gossip.

11:32.440 --> 11:35.080
You think I still care what they think?

11:36.880 --> 11:38.440
Do you think any of them would step in

11:39.720 --> 11:40.960
if I really make a move?

11:49.040 --> 11:49.880
Changning.

11:51.960 --> 11:54.320
When I asked you
if you pushed Hu, why did you nod,

11:55.120 --> 11:56.440
then shake your head?

11:59.840 --> 12:01.800
I did push him.

12:01.880 --> 12:04.360
But he's too heavy.

12:04.440 --> 12:06.240
I couldn't knock him over.

12:06.880 --> 12:08.360
He chased after me

12:08.440 --> 12:11.080
and fell down the steps on his own.

12:11.640 --> 12:13.680
That's how he broke his front teeth.

12:13.760 --> 12:15.640
-Hu says you pushed him.
-Shut up!

12:15.720 --> 12:18.040
I knew he fell by himself.

12:20.680 --> 12:22.040
Why did you push him?

12:23.320 --> 12:25.160
He pulled my hair.

12:26.000 --> 12:27.960
And snatched my candy away.

12:28.760 --> 12:31.360
And threw rice water at me.

12:31.440 --> 12:34.080
He called me the jinx's little sister.

12:35.240 --> 12:37.680
He said splashing water
would wash away the bad luck.

12:42.080 --> 12:44.360
You vicious old hag,
may you die without a coffin!

12:44.960 --> 12:46.160
You spew nothing but poison.

12:46.240 --> 12:48.120
Have you no virtue
to spare for your grandson?

12:48.200 --> 12:50.720
Aren't you afraid King Yama
will rip your tongue out?

12:50.800 --> 12:52.760
How have I no virtue?

12:52.840 --> 12:54.200
Did I kill her parents?

12:54.840 --> 12:58.160
Were all those deaths
in their family my doing?

12:59.040 --> 13:01.160
Everyone in Lin'an knows

13:01.240 --> 13:03.280
she's cursed.

13:03.360 --> 13:05.080
Only you and your old man,

13:05.160 --> 13:06.400
with no one left to bury you,

13:06.480 --> 13:09.160
would dare take in such a cursed family.

13:09.240 --> 13:11.880
Who knows? One day she may bring you
to your grave as well.

13:14.200 --> 13:15.600
If you ask me,

13:15.680 --> 13:18.680
the Fan family
should've left Xigu Alley long ago.

13:18.760 --> 13:21.440
What if one day
their enemies come knocking?

13:21.520 --> 13:22.360
How can you speak so viciously?

13:22.440 --> 13:24.120
Even if I am cursed,

13:24.200 --> 13:26.280
I'll drag you to your grave first,
you old crone.

13:26.880 --> 13:28.840
You want me out of Xigu Alley?
On what grounds?

13:29.440 --> 13:31.680
If you're so afraid, then you leave.

13:32.600 --> 13:33.440
One more thing.

13:36.640 --> 13:37.480
From now on,

13:38.280 --> 13:40.640
if you dare lay a finger
on Fan Changning again,

13:40.720 --> 13:42.720
whichever hand you use, I'll cut it off.

13:44.160 --> 13:45.840
You think I'm afraid of you?

13:47.080 --> 13:48.000
You don't scare me.

13:49.680 --> 13:50.560
Scare?

13:52.880 --> 13:55.560
I can cleave a pig's leg
in a single stroke.

13:56.840 --> 13:58.240
Your hand would be even easier.

13:59.280 --> 14:01.440
Left or right? Which hand
do you want to keep?

14:02.120 --> 14:03.480
-Or shall I take both?
-No.

14:04.440 --> 14:05.280
Hu!

14:06.480 --> 14:07.560
Hu--

14:08.240 --> 14:09.280
Grandma!

14:09.360 --> 14:10.400
That's karma.

14:11.200 --> 14:12.160
That's what you get.

14:12.760 --> 14:14.000
Everyone saw that, right?

14:14.080 --> 14:15.320
No one touched her.

14:15.400 --> 14:16.880
She fell on her own.

14:18.200 --> 14:21.480
It was her. She kicked me!

14:23.240 --> 14:25.560
-Kang…
-We all saw it.

14:25.640 --> 14:26.760
You fell by yourself.

14:26.840 --> 14:28.760
It's because you spew such wicked words

14:28.840 --> 14:30.080
that Heaven is punishing you.

14:30.720 --> 14:31.760
Exactly.

14:32.280 --> 14:34.840
It's that cursed Fan Changyu.
She's cursed me!

14:34.920 --> 14:37.040
Get lost, before I curse you
to your grave!

14:37.120 --> 14:38.960
Kang, take it slow.

14:39.040 --> 14:40.560
Careful you don't break your own teeth.

14:40.640 --> 14:42.640
And don't go blaming Changyu again.

14:48.360 --> 14:49.200
Changning.

14:50.560 --> 14:52.160
If anyone bullies you again,

14:53.000 --> 14:54.320
come tell me, all right?

15:24.440 --> 15:27.320
If you ask me,
don't wait for the New Year.

15:28.560 --> 15:29.520
You should leave now.

15:33.000 --> 15:34.720
Just because of a few rumors,

15:35.960 --> 15:37.520
you want to send me away?

15:40.000 --> 15:41.360
My family's troubles

15:42.080 --> 15:44.200
have already dragged you in twice.

15:46.920 --> 15:48.240
You don't owe me anything.

15:49.800 --> 15:52.440
The sooner you distance yourself
from my family,

15:53.520 --> 15:54.600
the safer you'll be.

16:02.840 --> 16:03.960
Do you believe what Kang said?

16:09.880 --> 16:10.720
No.

16:13.440 --> 16:14.520
I don't believe in fate.

16:15.760 --> 16:19.440
Nor do I believe anyone is born
under a calamity star.

16:20.280 --> 16:23.280
I just feel those people
won't let my family off easily.

16:25.960 --> 16:27.000
I won't drag you into this.

16:28.520 --> 16:29.920
You think pushing me away

16:31.120 --> 16:32.720
is for my own good?

16:34.720 --> 16:35.560
What about Ning?

16:36.880 --> 16:38.560
Will you cut ties with her too?

16:41.680 --> 16:42.520
No.

16:43.280 --> 16:44.240
She's too young.

16:45.160 --> 16:46.200
She needs me.

16:50.680 --> 16:51.520
So,

16:52.320 --> 16:53.720
I'm the only one you're driving away?

17:01.800 --> 17:03.840
You won't just swallow the insult.

17:05.079 --> 17:06.599
If someone splashes water on you,

17:06.680 --> 17:08.440
you deal with it on the spot.

17:12.160 --> 17:13.960
I once heard Mr. Wang say,

17:15.000 --> 17:16.079
"The law does not punish the masses."

17:17.720 --> 17:20.119
It means when too many people
break the law,

17:21.160 --> 17:23.560
the authorities can't punish them all.

17:24.359 --> 17:26.359
Now, the ones gossiping about me

17:26.440 --> 17:28.280
are practically the whole town.

17:28.359 --> 17:31.720
I can confront one person,
but can I confront everyone?

17:34.440 --> 17:36.120
YOUNG XIE ZHENG

17:40.560 --> 17:45.080
YOUNG WEI XUAN

17:47.240 --> 17:48.520
Then have you heard,

17:49.120 --> 17:50.680
"Kill the chicken to warn the monkey?"

17:50.760 --> 17:52.360
People are selfish by nature.

17:52.440 --> 17:53.800
If you appear weak,

17:54.680 --> 17:56.240
no matter how kind you are,

17:56.840 --> 17:58.240
no one will lend you a hand.

18:00.160 --> 18:01.920
But if you succeed,

18:02.640 --> 18:04.680
even if you do heinous things,

18:04.760 --> 18:07.120
crowds will rush to flatter you.

18:09.480 --> 18:12.440
Talk of ghosts and curses
only clouds people's judgment.

18:14.520 --> 18:16.440
Like that candy that hit Kang.

18:17.760 --> 18:18.680
In her view,

18:19.880 --> 18:21.560
it was ghosts and gods messing with her.

18:23.680 --> 18:25.280
I don't mind you saying this to me.

18:26.360 --> 18:27.600
But if you distance yourself

18:27.680 --> 18:29.880
from Mr. and Mrs. Zhao because of this,

18:30.560 --> 18:31.760
they'll be hurt.

18:37.400 --> 18:38.560
Then take what I said

18:39.360 --> 18:40.920
as a moment's impulse.

18:42.280 --> 18:43.240
Don't go.

18:45.360 --> 18:46.760
So I leave when you tell me to leave

18:47.400 --> 18:48.800
and stay when you tell me to stay?

18:49.800 --> 18:50.760
You've got some nerve.

18:53.880 --> 18:55.440
Don't be mad.

18:56.080 --> 18:58.240
The candy I bought you
wasn't meant for that.

18:59.040 --> 19:00.760
Maybe use small stones next time?

19:01.280 --> 19:03.920
Candy's expensive. Don't waste it.

19:13.920 --> 19:15.440
I never had the chance to ask.

19:16.840 --> 19:18.840
Why risk your life as an escort guard?

19:21.680 --> 19:22.680
Because

19:23.640 --> 19:25.160
I have things I must do.

19:26.360 --> 19:29.600
Just like how you want to continue
running your father's pork shop.

19:31.200 --> 19:32.080
My father

19:33.680 --> 19:35.080
also had unfinished wishes.

19:36.640 --> 19:38.080
I'll fulfill them for him.

19:41.960 --> 19:43.960
So your family runs an escort agency?

19:44.680 --> 19:46.000
You're the heir?

19:47.480 --> 19:49.880
Rebuilding an escort agency
would cost a fortune.

19:50.920 --> 19:52.480
When I earn enough,

19:52.560 --> 19:53.880
I can help you out.

19:54.480 --> 19:55.360
No need.

19:56.200 --> 19:57.440
I still haven't repaid you

19:57.520 --> 19:58.680
for saving my life.

20:00.200 --> 20:01.560
That's different.

20:02.520 --> 20:04.200
When you agreed to marry in,

20:04.840 --> 20:06.120
we were even.

20:07.920 --> 20:09.240
You want to be even with me?

20:13.120 --> 20:14.480
That's not what I meant.

20:26.280 --> 20:27.880
We've known each other this long,

20:27.960 --> 20:29.680
and I still don't know your birthday.

20:31.160 --> 20:32.800
My birthday's easy to remember.

20:32.880 --> 20:34.320
Two days after the Lantern Festival.

20:34.400 --> 20:37.240
The New Year spirit is still strong then,
lively and bright.

20:37.960 --> 20:38.800
What do you want?

20:41.920 --> 20:46.040
I just want the whole family together,
safe and sound.

20:46.720 --> 20:49.560
And when spring comes, it would be nice
to raise another litter of piglets.

20:58.000 --> 21:01.280
CAPITAL

21:01.360 --> 21:03.840
I have something to report.

21:04.480 --> 21:05.400
Grand Tutor, you may speak.

21:06.040 --> 21:06.880
Your Majesty.

21:06.960 --> 21:09.200
The weather has been erratic this year.

21:09.280 --> 21:12.200
Fields lie barren for miles,
and the crops have failed.

21:12.280 --> 21:14.440
In this year of calamity,

21:14.520 --> 21:17.280
if we continue sending
our grain reserves to the front,

21:17.360 --> 21:18.840
it may trigger a refugee crisis.

21:18.920 --> 21:21.680
It would shake the very foundation
of the state.

21:22.280 --> 21:24.720
I implore Your Majesty

21:24.800 --> 21:27.320
to recall the order
for provisions to the front lines.

21:27.400 --> 21:29.760
I beg Your Majesty to reconsider.

21:30.400 --> 21:33.280
The battlefront shifts by the hour.

21:34.000 --> 21:37.120
Even Marquis Wu'an has met defeat
on the battlefield.

21:38.160 --> 21:41.520
Before a decisive battle,
provisions are paramount.

21:42.080 --> 21:43.520
How can they be withdrawn so lightly?

21:43.600 --> 21:45.680
After years of war,

21:45.760 --> 21:47.360
the treasury is nearly depleted.

21:47.440 --> 21:48.440
It cannot bear further strain.

21:49.760 --> 21:50.880
If the treasury is empty,

21:50.960 --> 21:54.000
requisition grain locally
to meet the urgent need.

21:54.080 --> 21:56.360
Once Chongzhou is secured,

21:56.440 --> 21:59.240
we will repay the people.

21:59.320 --> 22:01.720
It is now winter,
and the New Year is near.

22:01.800 --> 22:04.720
The people barely have
enough grain as it is.

22:04.800 --> 22:05.880
If we requisition grain locally,

22:06.560 --> 22:09.960
Chancellor Wei, are you not concerned

22:10.040 --> 22:11.880
it will spark unrest among the people?

22:12.480 --> 22:14.400
The front lines are engulfed in war.

22:14.480 --> 22:16.600
The soldiers are locked in fierce combat.

22:16.680 --> 22:18.920
Provisions are the army's lifeline.

22:19.000 --> 22:20.520
How can the army go a day unfed?

22:21.240 --> 22:24.880
If the enemy uses this chance
to drive south and break our defenses,

22:24.960 --> 22:28.520
I fear it could bring ruin to the nation.

22:29.120 --> 22:34.520
Grand Tutor, do you dare
shoulder such a burden alone?

22:35.320 --> 22:36.560
Surely you do not

22:36.640 --> 22:39.280
wish to see a repeat
of the tragedy 16 years ago,

22:39.360 --> 22:41.600
when provisions failed to reach Jinzhou

22:41.680 --> 22:44.560
and the city was slaughtered.

22:57.280 --> 22:58.880
Chancellor Wei is far-sighted,

22:58.960 --> 23:01.640
truly Dayin's foremost loyal minister!

23:02.240 --> 23:04.320
Chancellor Wei is loyal and upright.

23:05.640 --> 23:09.640
WEI'S RESIDENCE

23:20.480 --> 23:24.440
Uncle, when I grow up, I want to fight
on the battlefield, just like Father.

23:39.160 --> 23:40.880
MRS. WEI

23:40.960 --> 23:42.040
My lord.

23:43.960 --> 23:45.200
Come in.

23:53.800 --> 23:55.440
Please have some ginseng tea.

24:01.000 --> 24:04.440
Zheng's remains have yet to be recovered?

24:08.560 --> 24:11.520
He bore the Wei family blood.

24:11.600 --> 24:15.560
He was raised under your careful guidance
from a young age.

24:16.440 --> 24:18.400
A mother's brother is as good as a father.

24:19.040 --> 24:22.320
For him to die like this is truly tragic.

24:22.400 --> 24:25.160
I hope you will take care of your health.

24:28.560 --> 24:30.920
-As for Xuan--
-Please return, my lady.

24:34.000 --> 24:35.800
I have spoken out of turn.

24:36.560 --> 24:38.280
I beg Your Excellency's pardon.

24:43.680 --> 24:45.280
I shall take my leave.

25:13.840 --> 25:16.240
Chancellor, Governor He Jingyuan of Jizhou

25:16.320 --> 25:18.120
has sent a brocade box by express courier.

25:19.840 --> 25:22.920
TO HIS EXCELLENCY, CHANCELLOR WEI OF DAYIN

25:28.400 --> 25:30.680
He has always been cautious.

25:33.120 --> 25:34.200
TO WEI QILIN

25:34.280 --> 25:35.280
To General Sui Tuo,

25:36.080 --> 25:37.160
Jinzhou is in danger.

25:37.240 --> 25:39.120
I must return due to urgent business.

25:39.200 --> 25:41.000
So I send my family general, Wei Qilin,

25:41.080 --> 25:44.520
bearing the Tiger Tally, to request
that you dispatch reinforcements.

25:44.600 --> 25:45.680
Hold Northern Jue at bay.

25:45.760 --> 25:47.240
Relieve Prince Chengde's peril.

25:48.040 --> 25:49.760
Central Commander, Wei Yan.

25:50.280 --> 25:52.960
Eighth day of the fifth month,
26th year of Taikang.

25:59.480 --> 26:01.720
It seems He Jingyuan

26:01.800 --> 26:04.480
means to risk his life to force me

26:04.560 --> 26:09.120
to spare the daughters
of those two traitors.

26:09.200 --> 26:10.400
He Jingyuan has some nerve.

26:11.000 --> 26:13.160
Chancellor, you should not
have shown mercy

26:13.240 --> 26:15.520
and called off the search
for Wei Qilin's body.

26:18.640 --> 26:19.920
Zheng

26:20.000 --> 26:22.560
suddenly reopened the investigation
into the Jinzhou massacre.

26:23.440 --> 26:25.440
Someone must be manipulating this
behind the scenes.

26:26.440 --> 26:29.840
Now even He Jingyuan no longer obeys.

26:29.920 --> 26:32.920
Shall I eliminate He Jingyuan?

26:35.760 --> 26:38.240
The battle at Chongzhou is at a stalemate.

26:38.320 --> 26:41.160
If we lose He Jingyuan, that blade,

26:41.240 --> 26:43.200
the northwest will be left exposed.

26:44.480 --> 26:46.000
-Understood.
-Let it be.

26:46.080 --> 26:47.600
They are only two girls.

26:48.680 --> 26:49.520
Let them be.

26:50.120 --> 26:52.240
What trouble could they possibly cause?

27:11.960 --> 27:12.960
Lord Li?

27:15.120 --> 27:17.200
Is your husband not at home today?

27:17.280 --> 27:18.440
HAVE A FULL MEAL

27:18.520 --> 27:19.800
He's out on business.

27:20.600 --> 27:21.600
Are you looking for him?

27:23.000 --> 27:25.040
Just asking. By the way,

27:26.400 --> 27:28.800
I've clarified everything
about your family's case.

27:29.920 --> 27:31.160
Who was responsible?

27:31.240 --> 27:33.920
The Jizhou authorities learned
the attacks stemmed from an escort

27:34.000 --> 27:36.040
your father handled years ago,

27:37.440 --> 27:40.000
rumored to concern a treasure map
left by the former dynasty.

27:41.160 --> 27:44.320
Over a decade ago,
the entire escort agency was massacred.

27:44.920 --> 27:46.840
Only your father survived.

27:46.920 --> 27:49.640
He later came to Lin'an Town
and lived quietly these past years.

27:50.480 --> 27:51.880
After the Chongzhou campaign,

27:52.600 --> 27:54.440
the treasure map was brought up again.

27:55.040 --> 27:57.360
The bandits of Qingfeng Stronghold
found your father.

27:57.440 --> 27:59.680
That's why they targeted your house
time and again.

28:01.280 --> 28:03.840
All for the sake of that treasure map.

28:03.920 --> 28:05.480
Treasure map?

28:07.680 --> 28:09.360
My parents have never mentioned it.

28:10.640 --> 28:11.480
Indeed.

28:12.680 --> 28:14.880
This is how rumors destroy lives.

28:18.040 --> 28:21.200
Why would Li Huai'an
invent such a story to close the case?

28:25.360 --> 28:26.240
My parents

28:27.640 --> 28:29.600
died because of a rumor?

28:32.960 --> 28:36.200
A few days ago,
word came from the Chongzhou rebels

28:36.760 --> 28:38.320
that they had found the map.

28:39.120 --> 28:41.160
The bandits won't return to town.

28:41.240 --> 28:42.640
You can rest easy.

28:45.200 --> 28:47.560
SPIRIT TABLET OF MENG LIHUA
SPIRIT TABLET OF FAN ERNIU

28:49.480 --> 28:51.800
If there's a chance
to capture those bandits

28:52.840 --> 28:56.360
and bring my parents justice,
I am at your disposal.

29:03.640 --> 29:05.760
Governor He of Jizhou, in his compassion,

29:06.600 --> 29:08.400
ordered me to deliver this money.

29:14.640 --> 29:15.560
This is all for me?

29:16.680 --> 29:18.920
The authorities have granted compensation

29:19.000 --> 29:22.040
to all families who lost kin
to the Qingfeng bandits.

29:22.120 --> 29:23.040
You are not alone.

29:24.040 --> 29:25.160
Ten taels per deceased.

29:25.240 --> 29:26.760
This is 30 taels of silver.

29:27.720 --> 29:28.720
Take it.

29:37.200 --> 29:39.440
The air is dry.

29:40.040 --> 29:42.480
Beware of fire.

29:46.760 --> 29:47.840
Here it comes!

29:49.280 --> 29:50.440
Changyu.

29:50.520 --> 29:53.120
-You talked in your sleep last night.
-What did I say?

29:54.800 --> 29:58.440
You said you were worried the spices
from other regions weren't authentic.

29:58.520 --> 30:01.480
And that five-spice wasn't enough,
you had to make it six.

30:02.200 --> 30:04.720
Then, you said if Zheng left,

30:04.800 --> 30:08.240
you'd never find
such a handsome husband again.

30:13.240 --> 30:14.440
Lower your voice.

30:17.280 --> 30:20.400
Changyu, we don't have to move now.

30:23.840 --> 30:27.920
But I already told everyone in the village
we were moving.

30:28.000 --> 30:30.680
If we don't move now, how embarrassing.

30:31.320 --> 30:34.160
What if we move out for a bit
and then move back?

30:34.240 --> 30:35.640
That still counts, doesn't it?

30:37.560 --> 30:39.040
Since when did you get so clever?

30:40.360 --> 30:43.560
Here's what you do.
Tell them we're not moving after all.

30:43.640 --> 30:45.160
Give them some candy,

30:45.240 --> 30:46.640
and they won't laugh at you.

30:47.200 --> 30:50.920
Changyu, when are you
moving back to Zheng's bed?

30:51.000 --> 30:52.600
You squeeze into my tiny bed every night.

30:52.680 --> 30:54.520
I can't even turn over.

30:55.120 --> 30:59.040
Mrs. Zhao says husband and wife
should share a bed for life.

31:00.840 --> 31:03.120
What, are you tired of me already?

31:03.720 --> 31:05.920
I don't care. I'm sleeping with you.

31:06.000 --> 31:07.000
Forever.

31:08.520 --> 31:09.400
Still tired of me?

31:09.480 --> 31:11.600
Go on, be tired of me. Still tired of me?

31:11.680 --> 31:13.800
-Not anymore!
-Still tired of me?

31:13.880 --> 31:15.760
-I'm not!
-Still tired of me?

31:15.840 --> 31:18.080
-Not tired of me now, right?
-I give up!

31:19.280 --> 31:21.240
-Then hurry and surrender.
-Changyu!

31:42.840 --> 31:43.840
All you do is eat.

31:44.720 --> 31:47.040
You're so fat,
I wonder if you can still fly.

31:56.400 --> 31:57.280
Off you go.

32:07.000 --> 32:10.040
XIGU ALLEY

32:10.120 --> 32:12.360
Let's go!

32:24.760 --> 32:25.640
Mrs. Fan, good morning.

32:27.040 --> 32:27.960
Morning.

32:35.800 --> 32:37.080
Lord Li.

32:37.840 --> 32:39.280
Why are you at the Song residence?

32:41.160 --> 32:43.560
I rented a vacant house through a broker.

32:43.640 --> 32:45.680
It turns out it's right across from yours.

32:47.280 --> 32:48.800
So the family here is surnamed Song?

32:50.600 --> 32:52.320
You're not returning to Jizhou?

32:52.400 --> 32:55.080
I promised I would find the one
who killed your parents.

32:55.160 --> 32:56.320
A promise must be honored.

33:04.880 --> 33:05.840
Lord Li.

33:10.560 --> 33:12.320
To catch the murderer,

33:12.400 --> 33:13.840
he's decided to stay for now.

33:13.920 --> 33:15.480
He happens to be renting Song Yan's house.

33:16.280 --> 33:17.480
Isn't that quite a coincidence?

33:19.080 --> 33:20.120
Indeed.

33:23.480 --> 33:24.720
I won't disturb you two.

33:37.960 --> 33:38.920
What's wrong?

33:39.000 --> 33:41.760
Our falcon is gone…

33:44.600 --> 33:46.720
Perhaps the lid wasn't fastened
last night.

33:46.800 --> 33:49.440
Once its wing healed,
it flew off on its own.

33:50.520 --> 33:52.720
A falcon belongs with its own kind.

33:52.800 --> 33:54.640
It must go back where it came from.

33:55.280 --> 33:56.320
Don't cry now.

33:57.800 --> 33:59.320
We can't keep it by force.

33:59.400 --> 34:01.440
It has its own kin as well.

34:02.280 --> 34:03.520
Don't cry.

34:05.240 --> 34:06.160
It will come back.

34:10.760 --> 34:13.719
Can you make a pinky promise with me,
on the falcon's behalf?

34:24.320 --> 34:25.840
You'll leave sooner or later,

34:27.679 --> 34:28.520
won't you?

34:30.440 --> 34:31.719
As things stand,

34:32.480 --> 34:33.800
to care for someone now

34:34.719 --> 34:36.159
would only bring her harm.

34:41.440 --> 34:42.360
People

34:43.080 --> 34:45.920
are not immortals without feeling.

34:46.920 --> 34:48.360
Matters of the heart

34:49.719 --> 34:50.639
are hard to control.

34:57.280 --> 34:58.480
Don't humor her.

34:59.120 --> 35:01.240
She's only feeling lonely.

35:01.320 --> 35:03.360
When spring arrives,
I'll buy her a basket of chicks.

35:03.440 --> 35:05.480
With new playmates,
she'll forget the falcon.

35:06.920 --> 35:07.840
When spring comes,

35:07.920 --> 35:10.680
I'll buy you a whole basket
of chicks, all right?

35:10.760 --> 35:13.040
No. I only want my falcon.

35:17.800 --> 35:19.960
-No?
-I'm not humoring her.

35:20.920 --> 35:23.440
To train a falcon,
you must first let it fly.

35:23.520 --> 35:26.600
The one that returns
is the one truly tamed.

35:29.160 --> 35:31.240
But what if it never comes back?

35:39.960 --> 35:41.360
WHERE THE HEART SOARS

35:41.440 --> 35:42.920
So you're really staying in Lin'an?

35:43.560 --> 35:46.080
When I heard, I was so happy
I couldn't sleep all night.

35:46.600 --> 35:48.760
Come see. I've been
getting this ready for so long.

35:49.360 --> 35:51.240
-Come.
-What is it?

35:53.720 --> 35:54.800
What are you doing?

35:54.880 --> 35:55.720
Look.

35:59.200 --> 36:00.320
The auspicious hour has come!

36:01.600 --> 36:03.280
FAN'S BRAISED MEAT

36:03.960 --> 36:05.360
PORK TRIPE, PIG'S EARS, PORK BELLY

36:20.160 --> 36:21.520
Excellent!

36:33.320 --> 36:35.280
A stick of incense for booming business.

36:48.120 --> 36:48.960
What's wrong?

36:50.280 --> 36:51.880
Nothing. Let's light the incense.

36:55.240 --> 36:57.960
Excellent!

37:05.040 --> 37:06.240
What would you like?

37:06.320 --> 37:07.920
Your meat smells wonderful.

37:08.000 --> 37:09.400
I'd like a lean piece.

37:09.480 --> 37:10.640
It's all lean and tasty.

37:11.320 --> 37:12.560
-Pick a big one.
-All right.

37:13.560 --> 37:14.760
Let me weigh it for you.

37:15.360 --> 37:16.960
-Come again.
-All right.

37:17.040 --> 37:18.360
Changyu, is that you?

37:18.960 --> 37:19.920
It's me.

37:20.000 --> 37:22.680
Your stall's been closed for days.

37:22.760 --> 37:25.160
We've had nowhere
to buy your braised pork.

37:25.240 --> 37:27.720
So you've brought your braised pork
to Yixiang Restaurant?

37:29.400 --> 37:32.240
Mrs. Fan's working
with Yixiang Restaurant now.

37:32.320 --> 37:34.560
From here on,
you'll only find her pork here.

37:34.640 --> 37:36.640
If you like it, come by often.

37:36.720 --> 37:40.960
Before, Changyu's pork
always came with offal.

37:41.040 --> 37:42.920
Then I'll help myself.

37:43.000 --> 37:43.920
Take a look at this.

37:44.000 --> 37:45.560
I… Well…

37:45.640 --> 37:46.720
This time…

37:46.800 --> 37:49.440
-No, this time…
-Changyu's braised pork

37:49.520 --> 37:50.680
used to be home-style.

37:51.440 --> 37:53.440
Now that she's with Yixiang Restaurant,

37:53.520 --> 37:56.160
the ingredients, seasoning, and recipe
have all been refined.

37:56.760 --> 37:58.200
Forget the offal,

37:58.280 --> 38:01.040
even the braising broth
is far richer than before.

38:04.040 --> 38:05.200
Then,

38:05.280 --> 38:07.360
how are common folk meant to afford it?

38:08.800 --> 38:10.120
Never mind.

38:10.200 --> 38:11.560
I'll try another place.

38:11.640 --> 38:14.080
It's our grand opening.
Let's start off on a lucky note.

38:14.160 --> 38:17.640
If you bring us five customers next time,

38:17.720 --> 38:18.880
you'll get 20% off.

38:19.600 --> 38:21.320
Ten customers, 25% off.

38:21.400 --> 38:23.680
Twenty customers, 30% off. How's that?

38:24.640 --> 38:25.480
All right then.

38:26.840 --> 38:27.840
Changyu,

38:27.920 --> 38:29.480
pick me two nice cuts.

38:29.560 --> 38:31.760
Today is my husband's birthday.

38:31.840 --> 38:33.120
Of course.

38:34.360 --> 38:36.680
I promise it'll be fragrant and generous.

38:36.760 --> 38:37.600
That one.

38:46.480 --> 38:47.800
I tried leaving out the offal.

38:47.880 --> 38:49.320
The customers weren't having it.

38:50.040 --> 38:52.560
A few words from you,
and they're lining up to pay.

38:52.640 --> 38:55.200
Qian, you've got a real knack
for business.

38:55.280 --> 38:56.960
Undercutting prices isn't business.

38:57.040 --> 38:58.400
Mutual gain is.

39:05.600 --> 39:08.840
"The noble man aligns his virtue with
Heaven and Earth,

39:09.760 --> 39:11.360
his light with the sun and moon,

39:11.880 --> 39:13.880
his conduct with the four seasons,

39:14.720 --> 39:16.840
and his destiny with Heaven's will.

39:18.120 --> 39:19.040
Before Heaven…"

39:39.160 --> 39:40.400
The Marquis graces us.

39:40.480 --> 39:42.160
I have not waited in vain.

39:44.120 --> 39:46.760
Speak. What brings you
to the Fan household?

39:50.040 --> 39:52.960
I came to the Fan household
only to see you.

39:57.400 --> 39:58.880
We've known each other since childhood.

39:59.720 --> 40:02.160
We both trained under General He.

40:03.960 --> 40:05.280
Since the Li-Wei feud began,

40:06.120 --> 40:08.000
we have avoided each other.

40:09.120 --> 40:11.560
Hard to believe it's been over a decade.

40:15.080 --> 40:16.880
Now I'm curious.

40:16.960 --> 40:20.000
Are you Li or Wei?

40:51.880 --> 40:55.240
I act only for Dayin and its people.

40:57.240 --> 40:58.080
What about you?

40:59.560 --> 41:00.560
Where do you stand now?

41:01.720 --> 41:04.400
Fine words are easy to say.

41:08.240 --> 41:10.600
I have always acted for myself.

41:12.880 --> 41:14.480
The Li-Wei feud has unsettled the court.

41:15.480 --> 41:18.320
If you now intend to stand apart
and form your own power,

41:18.400 --> 41:21.720
would that not throw the situation
into deeper chaos?

44:14.040 --> 44:16.880
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

44:16.960 --> 44:17.840
Subtitle translation by: Peng Peng
